{"tid":2198191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳文慧叫官勿同情襲警被告","createTime":"2020-09-11T07:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T07:39:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e619f7309552d8b4890525da864d250c0dd91b4e","tid":2198191,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/BKW4AAW2TJGXJOK2FRVLDXNRHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FBKW4AAW2TJGXJOK2FRVLDXNRHY%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=1414af03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FBKW4AAW2TJGXJOK2FRVLDXNRHY%2F&h=c54733a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/BKW4AAW2TJGXJOK2FRVLDXNRHY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n陳文慧叫官勿同情襲警被告<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gZY7J9S-CRR3SSraloGjUxIe3Fw=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FPOIJ5J5ORFJBK5R6EPF5PF7AU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgZY7J9S-CRR3SSraloGjUxIe3Fw%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFPOIJ5J5ORFJBK5R6EPF5PF7AU.jpg&h=0b394754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主控官陳文慧<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年10月27日市民在尖沙嘴梳士巴利花園舉行反警暴集會，聚集人群一度走出馬路，有部份市民辱罵警員，警方發射催淚彈驅散，其間一名退休的士司機被指在太空館對開推跌一名警署警長，被控襲警。案件已排期開審，惟昨再提訊時，被告選擇認罪，求情透露當日吸入催淚氣，接受洗眼時與警員發生爭拗，事後患上抑鬱。外聘主控官陳文慧則向主任裁判官嚴舜儀引述案例，「提醒」法庭不應給予同情考慮，應判監。最終被告遭判監兩星期。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n判監兩星期<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。，故被告取道該處往碼頭乘船。<br />\n<br />\n惟主控官陳文慧極力反駁說法。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n嚴官判刑指，相信被告最初無意傷及警員，但質疑他沒有另覓路綫前往碼頭，另無法判斷被告的精神問題是何時開始，但考慮他確受事件困擾等因素，判他監禁兩星期。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本案外聘主控為大律師陳文慧。本報早前報道，陳的fb賬戶發表大量「藍絲」言論，包括以「曱甴」形容示威者，更曾侮辱法官是人渣垃圾和「衰過狗」。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC468/20"},{"pid":"761840ac79706caa4b950b11540a7c1141f1c7b2","tid":2198191,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:39:32.000Z","msg":"政府教返個官?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}